extendedInfo.description: //////Jelly Bean (Android 4.1 and above) must also install the 'NST GO Contacts JB Patch'  to get it properly installed.//////Click below on 'More by star-E' to find it. It must be done AFTER installing this app to set the directories in which the assets will be installed. Sorry for the inconvenience....but it's still better than in-app purchasing.///After install don't press 'Open'. Also, don't use the shortcut icon GO Launcher creates. Just apply the theme in the GO Contacts settings.///Enjoy the look and feel of the computer displays in the new Star Trek movies (2009 and 2013 Into Darkness PCAP style to replace the standard LCARS). This theme is ideal for true fans or anyone who wants a sleek Sci-Fi look. Looks great on phones or tablets. (portrait and landscape)  This is also the most complete GO Contacts/Dialer theme on the market packed with the most images.*This theme is for Go Contacts Ex* You must have GO Contacts Ex installed to use it.Directions:This is a theme, so after installing don't press 'Open' just 'Done'.ãTo apply the theme, open the menu in Go Contacts Ex and tap "Themes" then find this theme and apply it.Also look for:New Star Trek Go Launcher ThemeNew Star Trek Keyboard ThemeNew Star Trek Go Locker ThemeNew Star Trek GOWidget ThemeNew Star Trek Go SMS ThemeNew Star Trek Live WallpaperNew Star Trek GO FontsNew Star Trek clock & battery skin (available free in Beautiful Widgets theme picker)*clock updated to v2*As you can see, I have a very complete theme pack to customize the whole phone / tablet for all parts of common use.To get informed when I release new Star Trek themes, follow me on twitter. @SethSteen or Facebook http://www.facebook.com/new.star.trek.theme Also, if you're a Trekkie I would appreciate it if you could support my work by clicking 'g+1' or sharing it on your social networks.If you like my work, PLEASE leave me a nice review to help me continue. Too many people never read the directions and leave a bad review saying, "It doesn't work".*If you are having trouble and the contact developer link isn't working, please contact me at seththomaslewis@gmail.com That is my personal email so I can get notifications right away and offer the fastest support.

reviews.title: Nicely done

reviews.title: Wow!
reviews.comment: This theme is not only very good looking but also actually an improvement on the basic contacts/dialer that I bad before. In your call log, it actually tells you how long your call was versus about how long ago you made it. I\'m just getting Star Trek, and after seeing the new movie last night, I thought it would be neat to have my phone look like something out of there, which is why I got a bunch of these themes. So far I\'m extremely happy with this. Well worth the purchase for me.

reviews.title: Amazing
reviews.comment: Night and day.  That\'s the difference between the look and feel of this theme to the default theme, or even any of the other Go Contact themes out there.  This high quality theme will be sure to make your device look as if you\'re accessing a terminal aboard the Enterprise.  So so so SIMPLE to install and apply.  All that is required is the ability to READ. I\'m so glad that everyone else who has purchased and reviewed this theme gave it the rating it deserves.  No illiterate trolls here.  Once again, star-E has produced a top quality app.
reviews.author: Tam Rachatanavin

reviews.title: NST Theme Suite Review
reviews.comment: Hey everyone, I have to say that this is an epically cool suite of themes you can download. They are amazingly aesthetically pleasing and they function really well. I love how you can customize the entire phone to be wholegrain NST awesome-sauce! Additionally, Seth (the creator) has amazing customer service. I\'ve had some questions here and there about settings and the like and he is on the reply immediately. Absolutely wonderful customer service, I couldn\'t be happier. I\'ll be paying attention for additional theme options,specifically hoping for a soundboard option from Seth. Thanks! Rob
reviews.author: Robert McDonell

reviews.title: Nerd heaven
reviews.comment: This collection of themes is awesome. You have to read the directions or you\'ll likely screw up the install but it\'s worth the time. Fun to customize the screens and impressed all my nerdy companions.... love it! Worth the money! Also great tech support from Seth!
